rt containing:\\n    - Resume-job match analysis\\n    - Interview summary\\n    - Technical assessment\\n    - Behavioral assessment\\n    - Strengths and weaknesses\\n    - Final recommendation and scoring breakdown\\n\\nThe workflow should support modular AI task execution and dynamic task delegation without hardcoded routing.\\n\\nProvide:\\n- Backend workflow architecture\\n- AI orchestration logic\\n- API structure examples\\n- Database schema suggestions\\n- Candidate scoring logic\\n- Example interview flows\\n- Example final evaluation reports\\n\\nThe output should be production-oriented and implementation-focused.\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nNo completed previous tasks context available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task2:\\n  Objective: Implement the Resume–Job Matching Module: parse and embed job descriptions and resumes, compute semantic similarity scores, and expose matching interface.\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Build the Interview Orchestration Engine: manage dynamic question flows, call AI services to generate technical and behavioral questions (including follow-ups), and track session state.\\nTask task4:\\n  Objective: Develop the Candidate Evaluation & Scoring Logic: analyze candidate responses for relevance, depth, confidence, and technical accuracy; compute composite scores across defined categories.\\nTask task5:\\n  Objective: Create the Email Generation Module: define templates and AI prompt flows for automated interview invitations and follow-up communications.\\nTask task6:\\n  Objective: Implement the Final Report Generation Module: assemble resume-job match data, interview summaries, technical and behavioral assessments, strengths/weaknesses, and recommendations into a structured report.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nDefine the database schema for job descriptions, candidate resumes, interview sessions, AI-generated questions, candidate responses, evaluation scores, email logs, and final reports.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nJSON schema\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"schemas\\\": {\\n    \\\"job_descriptions\\\": {\\n      \\\"type\\\": \\\"object\\\",\\n      \\\"properties\\\": {\\n        \\\"job_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Unique identifier for the job description\\\",\\n          \\\"primaryKey\\\": true\\n        },\\n        \\\"title\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Job title\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"description\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Full job description text\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"requirements\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Job requirements\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"responsibilities\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Job responsibilities\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"department\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Department the job belongs to\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"location\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Job location\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"date_posted\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"format\\\": \\\"date\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Date the job was posted\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"embedding\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\",\\n          \\\"items\\\": {\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"number\\\"\\n          },\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Vector embedding of the job description\\\"\\n        }\\n      },\\n      \\\"required\\\": [\\n        \\\"job_id\\\",\\n        \\\"title\\\",\\n        \\\"description\\\"\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    \\\"candidate_resumes\\\": {\\n      \\\"type\\\": \\\"object\\\",\\n      \\\"properties\\\": {\\n        \\\"candidate_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Unique identifier for the candidate\\\",\\n          \\\"primaryKey\\\": true\\n        },\\n        \\\"name\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Candidate's full name\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"email\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Candidate's email address\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"phone\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Candidate's phone number\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"resume_text\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Full text of the candidate's resume\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"skills\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\",\\n          \\\"items\\\": {\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\"\\n          },\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"List of skills extracted from the resume\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"experience\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Candidate's work experience\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"education\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Candidate's education details\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"embedding\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"array\\\",\\n          \\\"items\\\": {\\n            \\\"type\\\": \\\"number\\\"\\n          },\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Vector embedding of the resume\\\"\\n        }\\n      },\\n      \\\"required\\\": [\\n        \\\"candidate_id\\\",\\n        \\\"name\\\",\\n        \\\"email\\\",\\n        \\\"resume_text\\\"\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    \\\"interview_sessions\\\": {\\n      \\\"type\\\": \\\"object\\\",\\n      \\\"properties\\\": {\\n        \\\"session_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Unique identifier for the interview session\\\",\\n          \\\"primaryKey\\\": true\\n        },\\n        \\\"candidate_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Foreign key referencing candidate_resumes\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"job_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Foreign key referencing job_descriptions\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"start_time\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"format\\\": \\\"date-time\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Timestamp of when the interview started\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"end_time\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"format\\\": \\\"date-time\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Timestamp of when the interview ended\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"status\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"enum\\\": [\\n            \\\"scheduled\\\",\\n            \\\"in_progress\\\",\\n            \\\"completed\\\",\\n            \\\"cancelled\\\"\\n          ],\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Status of the interview session\\\"\\n        }\\n      },\\n      \\\"required\\\": [\\n        \\\"session_id\\\",\\n        \\\"candidate_id\\\",\\n        \\\"job_id\\\",\\n        \\\"start_time\\\"\\n      ]\\n    },\\n    \\\"ai_generated_questions\\\": {\\n      \\\"type\\\": \\\"object\\\",\\n      \\\"properties\\\": {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Unique identifier for the question\\\",\\n          \\\"primaryKey\\\": true\\n        },\\n        \\\"session_id\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"integer\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Foreign key referencing interview_sessions\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": {\\n          \\\"type\\\": \\\"string\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\